Remembered that Kanye sample song from one of the best albums. Then seeing his missed dunk at the Charlotte all star game reminded me of the best 1/2 time performance by someone in hip hop.

Leaving inspired. Hope everyone has a blessed 2020. Cherish all your blessings and lessons. #RIPKobe still has not gotten any easy.
